---
import CvLayout from '../layouts/CvLayout.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<CvLayout
  seo={{
    title: 'Volunteer in Kenya',
    description: 'Volunteer fundraising at Kayaba Educational Complex Center in the Mukuru slum, Kenya. Achieved over 225% of the crowdfunding goal.'
  }}
  breadcrumb="Volunteer in Kenya"
>
  <div class="cv-box cv-box--subpage">
    <div class="cv-subpage-header">
      <div class="cv-subpage-category"><Icon name="ph:tag" class="cv-subpage-category__icon" aria-hidden="true" /> Humanitarian project</div>
      <h1 class="cv-subpage-title">Volunteer in Kenya</h1>
      <div class="cv-subpage-meta">
        <p><Icon name="ph:map-pin" class="cv-subpage-meta__icon" aria-hidden="true" /> Mukuru slum, Kenya</p>
        <p><Icon name="ph:calendar" class="cv-subpage-meta__icon" aria-hidden="true" /> July, August & September 2015</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cv-subpage-content">
      <p>Kayaba Educational Complex Center is a school in the Mukuru Kayaba slum. As a fundraising volunteer, the goal was to help the school sustain its future by creating an online crowdfunding campaign. The campaign exceeded targets significantly, reaching over 225% of the initial goal with more than 600 shares. The funds were intended to finance new projects that would help the school achieve financial independence.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="cv-subpage-footer">
      <a href="/" class="cv-subpage-back"><Icon name="ph:arrow-left" class="cv-subpage-back__icon" aria-hidden="true" /> Retour à la page d'accueil</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</CvLayout>
